# Student Database Management System

## Overview
This project stores and manages student records in one place.  
It allows fast access, updates, and tracking of student data.

## Features
- Add new student records
- Update existing details
- Delete student data
- Search students by name or ID
- Store data using SQLite database
- Simple and user-friendly interface

## Tech Stack
- Python
- SQLite
- Tkinter (GUI)

## How to Run
1. Install Python  
2. Open terminal in project folder  
3. Run:
   python index.py

## Project Structure
- index.py → main application file  
- database.db → stores student records  

## Future Improvements
- Add login system  
- Export data to CSV  
- Add analytics dashboard  

